---

<Layout
  title="Swapnil Khalekar — AI Product Manager | GenAI, RAG, Agentic AI, Platform Modernization"
  description="AI Product Manager with 10+ years across enterprise SaaS and FinTech, building with GenAI, RAG, agentic systems, and platform modernization to drive measurable product outcomes."
>
  <section id="top" data-reveal class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(var(--card),0.86),rgba(var(--card),0.42))] px-6 py-8 shadow-[0_30px_120px_rgba(0,0,0,0.28)] sm:px-10 sm:py-12">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,rgba(var(--accent),0.22),transparent_30%),radial-gradient(circle_at_bottom_left,rgba(124,58,237,0.14),transparent_28%)]"></div>
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-y-0 right-0 hidden w-1/2 bg-[linear-gradient(transparent,rgba(var(--accent),0.06),transparent)] blur-3xl lg:block"></div>

    <div class="relative grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[1.25fr_0.75fr] lg:items-end">
      <div class="space-y-7">
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.7)] bg-[rgba(var(--bg),0.28)] px-4 py-2 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">
            <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-[rgb(var(--accent))]"></span>
            {profile.eyebrow}
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-4">
            <p class="text-base font-medium tracking-[0.02em] text-[rgba(var(--fg),0.94)] sm:text-lg">{profile.name}</p>
            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">{profile.title}</p>
            <h1 class="max-w-4xl text-4xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.04em] sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
              AI Product Manager who <span class="font-display italic text-[rgb(var(--accent))]">builds with AI</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="max-w-2xl text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.20em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))] sm:text-[0.95rem]">
              Product leadership · platform execution · hands-on experimentation
            </p>
            <p class="max-w-2xl text-base leading-8 text-[rgb(var(--muted))] sm:text-lg">
              I work at the intersection of product leadership, platform execution, and hands-on AI building. Across enterprise SaaS, FinTech, and side projects, I turn RAG, agentic workflows, and modernization efforts into shipped systems and measurable outcomes.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[rgb(var(--accent))] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 transition duration-200 hover:translate-y-[-1px] hover:opacity-95 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[rgb(var(--accent))]" href={`mailto:${profile.email}`}>
            Email Swapnil
          </a>
          <a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.75)] bg-[rgba(var(--bg),0.28)] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium transition duration-200 hover:border-[rgba(var(--accent),0.4)] hover:bg-[rgba(var(--card),0.7)] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[rgb(var(--accent))]" href={profile.linkedinUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            LinkedIn
          </a>
          <a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.75)] bg-[rgba(var(--bg),0.28)] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium transition duration-200 hover:border-[rgba(var(--accent),0.4)] hover:bg-[rgba(var(--card),0.7)] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[rgb(var(--accent))]" href={profile.githubUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            GitHub
          </a>
          <a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.75)] bg-[rgba(var(--bg),0.28)] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium transition duration-200 hover:border-[rgba(var(--accent),0.4)] hover:bg-[rgba(var(--card),0.7)] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[rgb(var(--accent))]" href={profile.cvUrl} download>
            Download CV
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.7)] bg-[rgba(var(--bg),0.24)] p-4 backdrop-blur">
            <div class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">10+</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">years across enterprise SaaS, FinTech, and AI automation</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.7)] bg-[rgba(var(--bg),0.24)] p-4 backdrop-blur">
            <div class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Builder</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">active side projects, AI experiments, and workflow tooling</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.7)] bg-[rgba(var(--bg),0.24)] p-4 backdrop-blur">
            <div class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Enterprise</div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">execution experience across India and European teams</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute -right-2 top-10 hidden h-28 w-28 rounded-full bg-[rgba(var(--accent),0.22)] blur-3xl sm:block"></div>
        <div class="absolute -left-6 bottom-10 hidden h-20 w-20 rounded-full bg-[rgba(124,58,237,0.18)] blur-3xl sm:block"></div>

        <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-sm">
          <div class="rounded-[2rem] border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.72)] bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(var(--bg),0.18),rgba(var(--card),0.62))] p-4 shadow-[0_25px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.35)]">
            <div class="rounded-[1.6rem] border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.6)] bg-[rgba(var(--bg),0.24)] p-3">
              <img src="/headshot.jpg" alt="Headshot of Swapnil Khalekar" class="aspect-[4/5] w-full rounded-[1.25rem] object-cover" loading="eager" decoding="async" />
            </div>
          </div>
            <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">building with AI tools, not just evaluating them from the outside</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="impact" data-reveal class="mt-8 grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-[1.25fr_0.75fr]">
    <div class="rounded-[1.75rem] border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(var(--card),0.72),rgba(var(--card),0.38))] p-6 sm:p-8">
      <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
        <div>
          <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">Selected impact</p>
          <h2 class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">A few outcomes that reflect how I work: practical, measurable, and tied to real product decisions.</h2>
          <div class="mt-6 text-5xl font-semibold tracking-[-0.05em] text-[rgb(var(--accent))] sm:text-6xl">{featuredImpact.metric}</div>
          <h3 class="mt-3 max-w-md text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-3xl">{featuredImpact.label}</h3>
          <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-sm leading-7 text-[rgb(var(--muted))] sm:text-base">{featuredImpact.context}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hidden rounded-full border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] px-3 py-1 text-xs text-[rgb(var(--muted))] sm:block">
          {featuredImpact.company}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-1">
      {supportImpact.map((item) => (
        <div class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] bg-[rgba(var(--card),0.42)] p-5 transition duration-200 hover:translate-y-[-2px] hover:border-[rgba(var(--accent),0.26)]">
          <div class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">{item.metric}</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-sm font-medium text-[rgba(var(--fg),0.92)]">{item.label}</div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">{item.context}</div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section data-reveal class="mt-24 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:items-start">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">Operating model</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">How I work when the problem is messy, technical, and worth solving.</h2>
      <p class="max-w-xl text-base leading-8 text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">
        I work best where product strategy, platform complexity, and execution reality overlap. I’m comfortable shaping direction at the roadmap level — and then dropping into the details, whether that means clarifying workflows, testing AI tools, or building side projects that sharpen my instincts about what actually works.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-4">
      {operatingModel.map((item) => (
        <div class="grid gap-4 rounded-[1.5rem] border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] bg-[rgba(var(--card),0.42)] p-5 sm:grid-cols-[auto_1fr] sm:items-start sm:p-6">
          <div class="inline-flex h-11 w-11 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.7)] bg-[rgba(var(--bg),0.3)] text-sm font-semibold text-[rgb(var(--accent))]">
            {item.step}
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight">{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-7 text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">{item.desc}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="experience" data-reveal class="mt-24 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.88fr_1.12fr] lg:items-start">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">Experience</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">A track record across AI automation, platform modernization, and product delivery at scale.</h2>
      <p class="max-w-xl text-base leading-8 text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">
        My background spans enterprise SaaS, FinTech, connected services, and platform-heavy product environments. Across roles, the pattern is consistent: reduce ambiguity, work close to the system, and ship product decisions that hold up in the real world.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-6 border-l border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] pl-6">
      {experience.map((item) => (
        <article class="relative rounded-[1.5rem] border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] bg-[rgba(var(--card),0.4)] p-6">
          <div class="absolute -left-[2.05rem] top-8 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.7)] bg-[rgb(var(--accent))]"></div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:justify-between">
            <div>
              <div class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">{item.dates}</div>
              <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">{item.company}</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-[rgba(var(--fg),0.92)]">{item.role} · {item.location}</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 sm:max-w-[16rem] sm:justify-end">
              {item.tags.map((tag) => (
                <span class="rounded-full border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] bg-[rgba(var(--bg),0.3)] px-3 py-1 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">{tag}</span>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>

          <ul class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">
            {item.highlights.map((highlight) => (
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="mt-[0.7rem] h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[rgb(var(--accent))]"></span>
                <span>{highlight}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </article>
      ))}

      <details class="rounded-[1.5rem] border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] bg-[rgba(var(--card),0.38)] p-6">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[rgba(var(--fg),0.9)]">Earlier experience</summary>
        <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
          {earlier.map((item) => (
            <div class="text-sm leading-7 text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">
              <div class="font-medium text-[rgba(var(--fg),0.92)]">{item.company} — {item.role}</div>
              <div>{item.desc}</div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section data-reveal class="mt-24 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:items-start">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">Lab / Side Projects</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">What I build to stay close to the tools, the workflows, and the reality of modern AI.</h2>
      <p class="max-w-xl text-base leading-8 text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">
        I use side projects as a working lab for product thinking, AI experimentation, and workflow design. Some are content-driven, some are tooling-focused, and some are infrastructure-heavy — but all of them help me stay grounded in how modern AI products actually get built.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-4">
      {labProjects.map((project) => (
        <a class="group rounded-[1.6rem] border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(var(--card),0.72),rgba(var(--card),0.35))] p-6 transition duration-200 hover:translate-y-[-2px] hover:border-[rgba(var(--accent),0.28)] hover:shadow-[0_20px_45px_rgba(0,0,0,0.18)] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[rgb(var(--accent))]" href={project.href} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">{project.title}</h3>
            <span class="text-sm text-[rgb(var(--muted))] transition group-hover:text-[rgb(var(--accent))]">↗</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">{project.desc}</p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {project.tags.map((tag) => (
              <span class="rounded-full border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] bg-[rgba(var(--bg),0.28)] px-3 py-1 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">{tag}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section data-reveal class="mt-24 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:items-start">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">Building in Public</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Notes, experiments, and product thinking shared along the way.</h2>
      <p class="max-w-xl text-base leading-8 text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">
        I write about AI experiments, side projects, and the practical gap between strategy and implementation. Some posts come from building tools, some from working through product problems in public, and some from learning where modern AI systems get interesting — or expensive.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
      {socialPosts.map((post) => (
        <a class="group rounded-[1.6rem] border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] bg-[rgba(var(--card),0.42)] p-6 transition duration-200 hover:translate-y-[-2px] hover:border-[rgba(var(--accent),0.28)] hover:shadow-[0_20px_45px_rgba(0,0,0,0.18)] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[rgb(var(--accent))]" href={post.href} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight">{post.title}</h3>
            <span class="text-sm text-[rgb(var(--muted))] transition group-hover:text-[rgb(var(--accent))]">↗</span>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">{post.summary}</p>
          <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            {post.tags.map((tag) => (
              <span class="rounded-full border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] bg-[rgba(var(--bg),0.28)] px-3 py-1 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">{tag}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
        </a>
      ))}
      <a class="sm:col-span-2 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-medium text-[rgb(var(--accent))] hover:opacity-90" href={profile.linkedinUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        Follow along on LinkedIn <span>↗</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="platforms" data-reveal class="mt-24 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:items-start">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">Platforms I’ve helped shape</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Selected public product context across AI, platform modernization, and connected systems.</h2>
      <p class="max-w-xl text-base leading-8 text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">
        These links point to public product or company pages for context. They are not case studies, but they do anchor the kinds of domains, platforms, and operating complexity behind the work.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
      {platforms.map((platform) => (
        <a class="group rounded-[1.6rem] border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(var(--card),0.72),rgba(var(--card),0.35))] p-6 transition duration-200 hover:translate-y-[-2px] hover:border-[rgba(var(--accent),0.28)] hover:shadow-[0_20px_45px_rgba(0,0,0,0.18)] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[rgb(var(--accent))]" href={platform.href} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
            <div>
              <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">{platform.org}</p>
              <h3 class="mt-2 text-xl font-semibold tracking-tight">{platform.title}</h3>
            </div>
            <span class="text-sm text-[rgb(var(--muted))] transition group-hover:text-[rgb(var(--accent))]">↗</span>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 inline-flex rounded-full border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] bg-[rgba(var(--bg),0.28)] px-3 py-1 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">
            {platform.label}
          </div>
          <p class="mt-4 text-sm leading-7 text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">{platform.desc}</p>
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section data-reveal class="mt-24 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr_1.1fr] lg:items-start">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">Credentials</p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Certifications and recognition that support the work — not replace it.</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-4">
      {certifications.map((cert) => (
        <div class="rounded-[1.4rem] border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] bg-[rgba(var(--card),0.4)] p-5 text-sm leading-7 text-[rgba(var(--fg),0.92)]">
          {cert}
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact" data-reveal class="mt-24 rounded-[2rem] border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.65)] bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(var(--card),0.84),rgba(var(--card),0.46))] px-6 py-8 shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.18)] sm:px-10 sm:py-10">
    <div class="grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] lg:items-end">
      <div>
        <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">Contact</p>
        <h2 class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
          If you’re building AI products that need to move from promise to production, let’s talk.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-base leading-8 text-[rgb(var(--muted))]">
          Best first step is email. One click. No form circus. No unnecessary friction. Just the useful part.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[rgb(var(--accent))] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 transition duration-200 hover:translate-y-[-1px] hover:opacity-95 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[rgb(var(--accent))]" href={`mailto:${profile.email}`}>
          Email me
        </a>
        <button type="button" data-email={profile.email} id="copy-email-inline" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.75)] bg-[rgba(var(--bg),0.28)] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium transition duration-200 hover:border-[rgba(var(--accent),0.4)] hover:bg-[rgba(var(--card),0.7)] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[rgb(var(--accent))]">
          Copy email
        </button>
        <a class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[rgba(var(--border),0.75)] bg-[rgba(var(--bg),0.28)] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium transition duration-200 hover:border-[rgba(var(--accent),0.4)] hover:bg-[rgba(var(--card),0.7)] focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[rgb(var(--accent))]" href={profile.cvUrl} download>
          Download CV
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
